## Business Value

The dashboard supports business decision-making by providing:

- Better visibility into sales performance.
- Identification of the most profitable products and regions.
- Customer performance analysis.
- Monitoring of key business KPIs.
- Faster access to business insights through interactive visualizations.

---

## Project Summary

This project demonstrates practical skills in business intelligence, data preparation, dashboard development, and business analytics using Microsoft Power BI.

The completed solution transforms transactional sales data into actionable insights that support strategic and operational business decisions.

---

## Future Improvements

Potential future enhancements include:

- Sales forecasting using predictive models.
- Customer segmentation analysis.
- RFM analysis.
- Customer Lifetime Value (CLV) analysis.
- Profitability forecasting.
- Advanced DAX calculations.
- Executive dashboard with drill-through functionality.
